  "detailed_description": "Oh, Dungeon Master is a dungeon simulator, with elements of a roguelike game. Explore intricate underground mazes and dense forests to exterminate monsters and find all the pictures! <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1708470/extras/f0faee19e889cef168de56d05aae097a.avif?t=1681551831\" width=620 height=200 /></span><br><br>The dungeons are full of dangerous monsters and valuable loot! Find the best armor and weapons, and stock up on healing potions before starting a fight with strong enemies.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1708470/extras/7f04815101e32f42cdf1eb5c00df8aab.avif?t=1681551831\" width=620 height=200 /></span><br><br>Oh, Dungeon Master is made in the style of an old-school RPG combined with new technologies. The game combines 3D Pixel Art with modern lighting and special effects to achieve the best image.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1708470/extras/ace764111c9197977d7691262d4eceb2.avif?t=1681551831\" width=620 height=200 /></span>",
  "about_the_game": "Oh, Dungeon Master is a dungeon simulator, with elements of a roguelike game. Explore intricate underground mazes and dense forests to exterminate monsters and find all the pictures! <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1708470/extras/f0faee19e889cef168de56d05aae097a.avif?t=1681551831\" width=620 height=200 /></span><br><br>The dungeons are full of dangerous monsters and valuable loot! Find the best armor and weapons, and stock up on healing potions before starting a fight with strong enemies.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1708470/extras/7f04815101e32f42cdf1eb5c00df8aab.avif?t=1681551831\" width=620 height=200 /></span><br><br>Oh, Dungeon Master is made in the style of an old-school RPG combined with new technologies. The game combines 3D Pixel Art with modern lighting and special effects to achieve the best image.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1708470/extras/ace764111c9197977d7691262d4eceb2.avif?t=1681551831\" width=620 height=200 /></span>",
